      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3>How does DETOX work?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            DETOX analyzes user-provided symptoms, medical history, and lifestyle data using complex algorithms to generate accurate predictions of potential diseases. It leverages machine learning and data-driven insights to enhance its predictive capabilities over time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3>How can DETOX benefit me?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            DETOX empowers individuals by providing early insights into potential diseases, allowing for proactive health management and timely intervention. It offers personalized recommendations, preventive measures, and lifestyle adjustments, helping users make informed decisions about their well-being.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3>Can I rely solely on DETOX for medical advice?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            DETOX is a supportive tool meant to provide insights and predictions. It should not replace professional medical advice or diagnosis. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional for personalized medical guidance and treatment options.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3> Is DETOX reliable in predicting diseases?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            DETOX has been developed and fine-tuned using extensive data and rigorous testing. While it strives for high accuracy, it's important to note that DETOX's predictions are based on available information and should not replace professional medical advice. Consultation with a healthcare professional is always recommended for an accurate diagnosis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3>Is my data secure with DETOX?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            Data security and privacy are top priorities for DETOX. It implements stringent security measures to protect user information, including encryption and strict access controls. DETOX adheres to relevant data protection regulations to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of user data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question">
          <h3>How do I use DETOX?</h3>

          <svg width="15" height="10" viewbox="0 0 42 25">
            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>

        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            Using DETOX is simple. Sign up for an account on the website, provide the required information such as symptoms and medical history, and let DETOX analyze the data. It will then generate predictions and recommendations based on the provided information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq">
